values:
i usually don't understand why people get stressed when the christmas season arrives. a haggard-looking mom out christmas shopping with kids in tow would probably give me an earful and altho i emphathize, i find christmas shopping to be fun even if it means jostling a bunch of shoppers in malls and elbowing my way to the prized gift items.&nbsp;i don't even mind 'burning' hard-earned money hehe, masaya kasi talaga mag shop for other people :D&nbsp; 

this year was different, like christmas suprised me na lang bigla. i feel unprepared and very un-christmassy. not really a grouch but i can't feel anything. 

maka shop nga para ma-feel ko ulit yung christmas adrenalin rush hehe.
